All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ExternalStandardMapping extends TypeDefElementHeader
ExternalStandardMapping defines a mapping of TypeDefs and TypeDefAttributes to an external standard. It includes the name of the standard, the organization that owns the standard and the equivalent type in the external standard. This mapping is done on a property type by property type basis. The aim is to create clarity on the meaning of the open metadata types and support importers and exporters between open metadata types and external standards.
